==English==
===Etymology===
Abbreviation of '''[[electronic mail]]'''.

===Variant spellings===
*[[email]]

===Noun===
'''e-mail''' (''[[countable]] and [[uncountable]]''; ''plural'' '''e-mails''')

#(''uncountable'') A system for transferring messages from one [[computer]] to another, usually via a [[network]].
#:''He sent me his details via e-mail.''
#(''countable''; ''also'' '''e-mail message''') A message sent by this system.
#:''I am searching through my e-mails.''

===Adjective===
'''e-mail''' (A-mI')

#A moderate bluish-green to greenish-blue
#:''I don't believe that e-mail skirt suits you.''

